			"updated": 1772477437455,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "Dashed boxes = OVS bridges. \nTest traffic via Raikou OVS. \nSeparate productivity/streaming servers \nenable L7 path steering (route via different WAN paths). \n\nManagement: Docker 192.168.55.0/24.",
