			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"baseline": 32,
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "Dashed boxes = OVS bridges. \nTest traffic via Raikou OVS. \nSeparate productivity/streaming servers \nenable L7 path steering (route via different WAN paths). \n\nManagement: Docker 192.168.55.0/24.",
